title: Welcome Mr. Moody, Regression For Henry?
description:
Matthew Berry and Daniel Dopp officially welcome Eric Moody in person to the 06010 to discuss if Russell Wilson really has a path to being the top scoring QB this season. Plus, we get an explanation from Eric on his running back ranks including why he is much lower on Derrick Henry than Matthew.
